member.example:
To add a case to an existing SPSS file called mydata.sav, the following code could apply:

using( SpssDataDocument doc = SpssDataDocument.Open("mydata.sav", SpssFileAccess.Append) )
{
	SpssCase Case = doc.Cases.New();
	Case["var1"] = 5;
	Case["var2"] = 3;
	Case["name"] = "Andrew";
	Case.Commit();
}

